{
  "stem": "25423.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that I was taught, and I'm a very quick learner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had to learn, first of all, mannerisms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have to-- I had to learn, very quickly, the language, and the ways of Ukrainian prayers, and behave in the church.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never went to the sacraments, but I had to make the right moves and the rhythm of what was going on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- I am not a Catholic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't want to-- respect-- they told me not to go to sacraments because of blasphemy, because they believe that the host is the body and-- of Christ.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not in my mind at that time because the question was the survival from day to day, from hour to hour.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in a variety of monasteries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but the first one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first one, I would say probably close to 30.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably two months or three months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After three months, I was sufficiently trained that I could sing in the choir with them, learned old Slavonic, because they play in old Slavonic, and participate in all of the ceremonies without any problem.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They treat me-- they treated me the same way as they treat me today.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In their minds, I am one of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they treat me-- treated me as a friend, as part of the community.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "17, 18.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was treated the same way as I-- as everybody else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked with them, as everybody else, which was not easy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very hard life, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We faced the danger the same way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all I can say, curiously enough, I said in-- old conscience today, from perspective of 71 years of life and other experience, these were the happiest days of my life.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
